item.title: About
item.description: Essay Write a Statement of Purpose up to 500 words on why you are applying to participate in a 360 International semester exchange. Your statement should include the following: The reasons why you would like to participate in an exchange (i.e. personal motivations, academic/professional benefits). Why you would be a suitable representative for the University of Auckland. Any additional information about why you have listed particular host universities in your application, if unable to fit this into the space provided on the Host University Preferences & Proposed Courses form.
